# Fonts are fetched on demand via `npm run fetch-fonts`. The downloaded files
# come from the official Google Fonts repository (Montserrat Alternates, SIL
# OFL 1.1) — they are not committed to keep the source tree clean and free
# of any specific font-distribution license obligations beyond the OFL.txt
# that travels with the fetched files.
src/fonts/*.ttf
src/fonts/*.otf
src/fonts/OFL.txt
